<subSubSection id="A5B74B72D137B085E404096D3F5C6301" pageId="0" pageNumber="201" type="notes">
<paragraph id="1942C69591B1048312C617C4075A79F3" pageId="0" pageNumber="201">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="28D60C681D23D00EA61197EC08AA717C" pageId="0" pageNumber="201">
New record for the Maltese Islands. The above material belongs to the nominate subspecies 
<taxonomicName id="7D2EFFB1B1ECCBD56402E69DB8C465B7" authority="ephippium" class="Insecta" family="Vespidae" genus="Parodontodynerus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Parodontodynerus ephippium subsp. ephippium" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="201" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="ephippium" subSpecies="ephippium">
<emphasis id="B038A64DA682883E43FBEA337FBC3E7C" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="201">Parodontodynerus ephippium ephippium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Klug, 1817) which is present throughout southern Europe, as well in Southwest Asia to Iran (
<bibRefCitation id="3F4719F11C0E94BD0B281423721A6EC3" author="Gusenleitner, J" journalOrPublisher="Eos Madrid" pageId="0" pageNumber="201" refId="B15" refString="Gusenleitner, J, 2000b. Bestimmungstabellen mittel- und suedeuropaeischer Eumeniden (Vespoidea, Hymenoptera) Teil 14. Der Gattungsschluessel und die bisher in dieser Reihe nicht behandelten Gattungen und Arten. Linzer Biologische Beitraege 32/1: 43-65." title="Bestimmungstabellen mittel- und suedeuropaeischer Eumeniden (Vespoidea, Hymenoptera) Teil 14. Der Gattungsschluessel und die bisher in dieser Reihe nicht behandelten Gattungen und Arten. Linzer Biologische Beitraege 32 / 1: 43 - 65." year="2000 b">Gusenleitner 2000b</bibRefCitation>
). In the Maltese Islands, this species seems to be most active between the warm months of May and July.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
